  "name": "screen-resumes-with-ai-alert-recruiter-email-shortlisted-candidates",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: screen-resumes-with-ai-alert-recruiter-email-shortlisted-candidates",
  "category": "AI",
  "tags": [
    "n8n advance",
